["Alessondria Lovelyn"] = {["language"]="English", ["race"]="Breton", ["class"]="Sorcerer", ["lore"]="LANGUAGE: English\nAGE: between 17-19\nRACE: half breton half altmer\nPERSONALITY: Entitled, prissy, neat, aloof\nCURRENTLY: Sweating from the heat, adorned in loose fitting and moderatly revealing clothing.\n\nAlessondria is a pleasing to look at youthful breton woman with golden eyes and blonde hair tied into a forward braided pigtails. She wears some makeup, especially around her eyes and lips. The young woman smiles often and its a pretty disarming look. Her movments are graceful and clearly some of her body language is of the high elven style.\n\n// more into dominant female breton or altmers"},
