["Mulic"] = {["language"]="English", ["race"]="Argonian", ["class"]="Nightblade", ["lore"]="Before you stands an Argonian, \"Mulic\" almost certainly not his real name but one he has adopted.\n\nHis scales  pale, his eyes vile. His stance that of an acrobat but his demeneur that of something much darker.  \n\nHe dons the clothing of that of a Dark Brother from the infamous murderers guild.\n\nHe seems introverted, as if he would rather slip past a crowd than walk through it, Not likely the kind to have many friends, or to want them.\n\nTo the intuitive this argonian seems off, The pale complexion and the darkness that seems to follow him,  Trouble maybe? or just another vile beast that needs slain.\n\n"},
